```{r pancreas 32641744, include=FALSE}

PMID_32641744 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32641744', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32641744 <- paste0(PMID_32641744$journal,' ', PMID_32641744$year, ' ', PMID_32641744$month,';', PMID_32641744$volume,'(', PMID_32641744$number,'):', PMID_32641744$pages)

PubMed_32641744 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32641744$eprint)

doi_32641744 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32641744$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
